data.description: Just 10 miles from SJAFB this home is ready for you to move right in. The homeowners have freshly professionally painted kitchen cabinets and misc. walls to create a welcoming environment. split floor plan with 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms. This home has been immaculately cared for. Open floor plan from kitchen, dinning and living room that has beautiful hard wood flooring and electric fireplace.  Laundry Room and 2 car attached gargage. Large privacy fenced in yard and beautifully painted back deck makes you feel like it is summer all year long. Home has Solar Panels installed to help in reduction of the utility bill. Do not miss your opportunity to view this beautiful warm inviting home.
